<Input><Text-field style="Normal" layout="Normal">Generators: serial groups</Text-field><Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">ct:=time(): for n from 1 to 3 do
 FG_equal(C||n||d,FG_group([PG_sh.PG_c(2*n)],2*n));
 FG_equal(S||n   ,FG_group([PG_sh.PG_c(n)  ],2*n));
 FG_equal(C||n||v,FG_group([ PG_c(n),PG_sv ],2*n));
