#OBS:=map(v-&gt;piecewise(v[1]=&quot;H&quot;,&quot;S&quot;,member(v[1],[&quot;C&quot;,&quot;N&quot;,&quot;O&quot;,&quot;F&quot;]),&quot;S,X,Y&quot;,&quot;&quot;),FD):
OBS:=map(v-&gt;piecewise(member(v[1],[&quot;C&quot;,&quot;N&quot;,&quot;O&quot;,&quot;F&quot;]),&quot;Z&quot;,&quot;&quot;),FD):
#OBS:=[&quot;Z&quot;,&quot;Z&quot;,&quot;&quot;,&quot;&quot;,&quot;Z&quot;,&quot;&quot;,&quot;Z,YZ,ZX&quot;]:
#OBS:=[&quot;S,X,Y&quot;,&quot;&quot;]:
#OBS:=[&quot;A&quot;,&quot;S&quot;]:
OBS:=map(v-&gt;`if`(v=[&quot;&quot;],[],v),map(v-&gt;Split(v,&quot;,&quot;),OBS));
osb2B:=(o,s,b)-&gt;sprintf(&quot;%s%d%s&quot;,FD[o][1],orbs[o][s],b):
B2osb:=table([seq(seq(seq(osb2B(o,s,b)=[o,s,b],b=OBS[o]),s=1..nops(orbs[o])),o=1..no)]):
BS:=map(osb2B@op,Sort([entries(B2osb,nolist)],v-&gt;orbs[v[1]][v[2]]*nops(A)+SearchPos(SBS,v[3])));
N:=nops(BS);
B2k:=table([seq(BS[k]=k,k=1..N)]):
ou2lsk:=(o,u)-&gt;[seq(seq(B2k[osb2B(o,s,b)],b=Split(u,&quot;;&quot;)),s=1..nops(orbs[o]))]:</Text-field>
